                    </div>
                    <div className="col-md-5 feature-box"><i className="icon-refresh icon"></i>
                        <h4>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Calculations</h4>
                        <p>TVA calculations and loans and other calculations&nbsp;</p>
